title: Is American Cheese Really Cheese?
description:
Is American cheese a worthy representative of these United States on your charcuterie board, or a chemically derived imposter? Today, Josh and Nicole are debating: 'is American cheese really cheese?' on this episode of A Hotdog Is A Sandwich.
